  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[When Digivolving] Delete 1 of your opponent''s Digimon
    with 6000 DP or less. For every Digimon your opponent has in play, add 2000 to
    the maximum this DP-based deletion effect can delete. [All Turns][Once Per Turn]
    When an opponent''s Digimon is deleted, if you have a Tamer in play, delete 1
    of your opponent''s Digimon with the highest DP.'
